title: Kenwood KNA-DV4100 Navigation USA East 2007 Update Map DVD
description: Since i don&#039;t think kenwood sold any update discs for the KNA-DV4100, I went ahead and made my own. Since 3/4 of all nav systems use denso, it was just a matter of using a recent disc, in this case from a GM and changing the headers to match those of an existing kenwood disc. This should give you maps and POI as of 2007 and seems to work so far. This is a disc for the eastern half of the USA/Canada. Don&#039;t forget that you have to burn this as a DVD-ROM, so something like ImageBurn should have no problem with it. Enjoy!
